snippet.description:

Download my games for Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/dev?id=7741067125244845113 Fly the world with an arcade 2d flight simulator.

mobile - Get it here (Play Store): https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.PhrsSoftware.FlightSimulator2D

pc/mobile - Or here (itch.io): https://phstsoftware.itch.io/2d-flight-simulator

- Boeing 737

- Boeing 747
And more

- Flaps
- Landing Gear
- Reverser
- Speed Brakes
And much more.
